      • getCombinedSelectorList

        public static com.google.common.collect.ImmutableList<ICSSSelector> getCombinedSelectorList(ICSSSelector selector)
        Convert the selectors chained by combinators into a list of simple selectors ordering from ancestors to descendants.

        For example: s|HBox s|VBox s|Label
        will be converted to:
        List { HBox, VBox, Label }

        Parameters:
        selector - The subject selector in a descendant selector chain.
        Returns:
        A list of selectors.
